<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password - {{appName}}</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your {{appName}} account. Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
    <p>
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
            Reset Password
        </a>
    </p>
    <p>If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>{{appName}} Team</p>
</body>
</html>